Ronson also played guitar on the number.  Ronson is the white DJ shown at the beginning of this clip.  Coldplay is a British band, and Chris Martin is the vocalist. He is the white guy between Beyonce and Mars at the end. Coldplay was hired for the Superbowl halftime show. Martin came up with the idea of Mars and Beyonce appearing. Mars initially didn't want to, but Beyonce did. Mars eventually agreed. Beyonce sings her song, "Formation," from the Lemonade album, suitably edited. Her ladies are dressed like Black Panthers. Although it looks like Martin is barging in at the end, you can see that Beyonce and Mars back up to invite him to join them. Everybody is a class act.
